ux A)\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=52|off=neg}}\n|52-\n|6\n|[[BBC]] (Mux B)\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=53}}\n|53\n|500\n|[[Channel 4]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=57}}\n|57\n|500\n|[[BBC One]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=60}}\n|60\n|500\n|[[ITV Central|Central]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=63}}\n|63\n|500\n|[[BBC Two]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=68}}\n|68\n|10\n|[[Digital 3&4]] (Mux 2)\n|DVB-T\n|}\n\n====June 1999 \u2013 April 2009====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!{{no2}}Frequency\n!{{no2}}UHF\n!{{no2}}kW\n!{{no2}}Service\n!{{no2}}System\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=29}}\n|29\n|8\n|[[Arqiva]] (Mux D)\n|[[DVB-T]]\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=34}}\n|34\n|10\n|[[BBC]] (Mux 1)\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=47}}\n|47\n|\u2014\n|[[Six TV]] <small>(The Oxford Channel until 2003)</small>\n|[[PAL]] System I\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=48}}\n|48\n|8\n|Arqiva (Mux C)\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=49}}\n|49\n|40\n|[[Channel 5 (UK)|Channel 5]]\n|[[PAL]] System I\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=51|off=neg}}\n|51-\n|6\n|[[S4C Digital Networks|SDN]] (Mux A)\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=52|off=neg}}\n|52-\n|6\n|[[BBC]] (Mux B)\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=53}}\n|53\n|500\n|[[Channel 4]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=57}}\n|57\n|500\n|[[BBC One]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=60}}\n|60\n|500\n|[[ITV1]] <small>(Central until 2002)</small>\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=63}}\n|63\n|500\n|[[BBC Two]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=68}}\n|68\n|10\n|[[Digital 3&4]] (Mux 2)\n|DVB-T\n|}\n\n====April 2009 \u2013 14 September 2011====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!{{no2}}Frequency\n!{{no2}}UHF\n!{{no2}}kW\n!{{no2}}Service\n!{{no2}}System\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=29}}\n|29\n|8\n|[[Arqiva]] (Mux D)\n|[[DVB-T]]\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=34}}\n|34\n|10\n|[[BBC]] (Mux 1)\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=48}}\n|48\n|8\n|Arqiva (Mux C)\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=49}}\n|49\n|40\n|[[Channel 5 (UK)|Channel 5]]\n|[[PAL]] System I\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=51|off=neg}}\n|51-\n|6\n|[[S4C Digital Networks|SDN]] (Mux A)\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=52|off=neg}}\n|52-\n|6\n|[[BBC]] (Mux B)\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=53}}\n|53\n|500\n|[[Channel 4]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=57}}\n|57\n|500\n|[[BBC One]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=60}}\n|60\n|500\n|[[ITV1]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=63}}\n|63\n|500\n|[[BBC Two]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=68}}\n|68\n|10\n|[[Digital 3&4]] (Mux 2)\n|DVB-T\n|}\n\n====14 September 2011 \u2013 28 September 2011====\nBBC Two closed on UHF 63 on 14 September 2011. Channel 4 temporarily moved into its frequency at the time to allow BBC A to launch on UHF 53. The remaining analogue signals ceased on 28 September.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!{{no2}}Frequency\n!{{no2}}UHF\n!{{no2}}kW\n!{{no2}}Service\n!{{no2}}System\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=29}}\n|29\n|8\n|[[Arqiva]] (Mux D)\n|[[DVB-T]]\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=34}}\n|34\n|8\n|Arqiva (Mux C)\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=49}}\n|49\n|40\n|[[Channel 5 (UK)|Channel 5]]\n|[[PAL]] System I\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=51|off=neg}}\n|51-\n|6\n|[[S4C Digital Networks|SDN]] (Mux A)\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=52|off=neg}}\n|52-\n|6\n|[[BBC]] (Mux B)\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=53|off=pos}}\n|53+\n|100\n|[[BBC]] A\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=57}}\n|57\n|500\n|[[BBC One]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=60}}\n|60\n|500\n|[[ITV1]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK System I|ch=63}}\n|63\n|500\n|[[Channel 4]]\n|PAL System I\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=68}}\n|68\n|10\n|[[Digital 3&4]] (Mux 2)\n|DVB-T\n|}\n\n===Digital television 2011 \u2013 2018===\n\n====28 September 2011 \u2013 18 April 2012====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!{{no2}}Frequency\n!{{no2}}UHF\n!{{no2}}kW\n!{{no2}}Operator\n!{{no2}}System\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=53|off=pos}}\n|53+\n|100\n|[[BBC]] A\n|[[DVB-T]]\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=55}}\n|55\n|12.5\n|[[Arqiva]] B\n|DVB-T\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=57}}\n|57\n|100\n|BBC B\n|[[DVB-T2]]\n|-\n|{{UK DVB-T|ch=59|off=neg}}\n|59-\n|12.5\n|Arqiva A\n|DVB-T\n|-\